		    =-=-=- Assassin -=-=-=

	The Assassins are semi spell casters who have
trained in skills that are appropriate for covert operations.
They specialize in assassination, spying and infiltration;
and have distinct spells affecting their abilities to move
and distract. Their skills specialize in disguises, poisons,
and deady weapons.

Type:   Semi Warrior
Skills: Assassination, Poison, Stealth type skills
Spells: Illusions, Movement, Poison
Prime Attributes: Int, Dex

Examples: Picture a Ninja. Now picture a Ninja who can cast 
	spells. Now picture him coming after... YOU!
Comments: The Assassins are very skilled assassins and spys.
	This guild is powerful in its specialized areas, and
	is a force to be feared.
